</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="mt-16 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <Feather className="w-5 h-5 text-zinc-400" /> Introduction
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque at velit nec nunc efficitur sodales. Sed facilisis dignissim tellus non congue. Nulla facilisi. Fusce vitae augue vel lorem tristique lacinia. Morbi ac nisi eu diam iaculis sodales. Vivamus porta ligula eget lectus tincidunt, non gravida massa facilisis. Curabitur congue, sapien a commodo mattis, lectus libero luctus urna, in sodales justo est sed leo.
